author: felicity
msg: bug 3976: rework how uris are parsed out of the message.  the urirbl plugin now orders the domains to query, based on where in the message the uri was found.  separate out anchor uris which have text between open and close and those that don't.  removed uri html metadata since there is now a different/better way to get it.
